
WHAT IS PYTHON :-

Python is a high-level, interpreted, and general-purpose programming language used to build software,
websites, automation scripts, and data science applications. It is known for its simple syntax and
easy readability, which makes it a good language for beginners as well as professionals.

Key Features of Python :-

Easy to Learn and Read – Python uses simple English-like syntax.

Interpreted Language – Code runs line by line, so debugging is easier.

Platform Independent – Python programs run on Windows, Linux, and macOS.

Large Standard Library – Python provides many built-in modules and tools.

Object-Oriented – Supports classes and objects for structured programming.

Open Source – Free to use and supported by a large community.


Applications of Python :-

Web development

Data science and machine learning

Automation and scripting

Desktop applications

Game development

Artificial Intelligence




















